summary: Completed comprehensive testing of SlotSwapper peer-to-peer scheduling application. Backend APIs are fully functional with 100% test pass rate. Frontend UI and integration working correctly with minor accessibility warnings.

design_issues.issue: Missing Description or aria-describedby attributes for accessibility

passed_tests: User signup with name, email, password, and timezone
JWT token persistence across page refresh
Create new events with title, start time, end time, and status
View all user events in dashboard
Update event status from BUSY to SWAPPABLE and vice versa
Marketplace: View swappable slots from other users
Request swap: Select opponent's slot and offer own swappable slot
Protected routes: Unauthenticated users redirected to login
Navigation between Dashboard, Marketplace, and Notifications
Backend swap request creation and management
Error handling for unauthorized access and duplicate emails
